# Event Scheduling & Resource Allocation System

This project is developed as part of the Flask Hiring Test for
Aerele Technologies Private Limited.

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- HTML/CSS

## Features
- Create and manage events
- Create and manage shared resources
- Allocate resources to events
- Prevent resource double-booking using conflict detection
- Generate resource utilisation report

## Conflict Detection Logic
The system checks time overlap before allocating a resource:
- Partial overlap
- Full overlap
- Nested time intervals

## How to Run
```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python run.py
